&lt;p&gt;While we’ve raised $30MM+ to date from some of the world’s best investors, we’re profitable with a strong balance sheet and an indefinite runway. We pride ourselves on achieving rapid growth without having to incinerate capital.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Our Products&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apartmentiq.io/&quot;&gt;ApartmentIQ&lt;/a&gt; is the all-in-one data platform powering smarter decisions across multifamily—covering 40M units with daily property and market intelligence used for surveys, research, and revenue management. We&#39;re trusted by 65% of the NMHC Top 50. Our sister company, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hiremaven.ai/&quot;&gt;MavenAI&lt;/a&gt;, delivers AI-powered marketing automation built by industry experts and integrated directly with property management systems, serving over 2M units.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a strategic and successful Account Executive to join us in bringing our rapidly growing ApartmentIQ product suite to multi-family owners, operators, and ancillary stakeholders. You’ll have a direct impact on the expansion of our business and be recognized and rewarded for your success. We only hire the best, and you’ll need to convince us that you’re a top-level performer. To succeed, you’ll need to be comfortable in a hunting role, building your pipeline from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the entire sales cycle: from account-level strategy development to prospecting to close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct a high volume of emails, calls, Zoom, and limited in-person presentations to secure new business&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate all proposals, pricing, and contract negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish meaningful relationships with customers, serving as their original point of contact and multifamily expert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with sales development and customer success teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nurture customer accounts through an onboarding and sales conversion process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the ApartmentIQ brand in your active markets and at industry events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a sales pipeline, sales forecast, and activity tracking within Salesforce CRM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet and exceed performance metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel as required for industry events and customer meetings (up to 25%)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
