&lt;p&gt;The goal is not just to increase AI usage. The goal is to help every team build the muscle for using AI instinctively, safely, and effectively to move faster, improve quality, and create more operating leverage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for someone with high agency, strong judgment, and a builder mindset, someone who can turn ambiguous operational problems into practical AI workflows that people actually use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
